STEP 6: When all errors fixed → git commit
STEP 7: Run `node scripts/security-attack-test.js` → 1000-pass attack simulation
STEP 8: If any attack test fails → go back to STEP 3
STEP 9: All 1000 attack tests pass → git commit + update SESSION_STATE.md → DONE
